data.title: Parking sucks and is limited
data.text: Besides parking issues, great Starbucks. Staff of every Starbucks is generally nice. The interior is nice and roomy. Only issue is the parking lot is small!

data.title: Consistent coffee
data.text: What more can be said about Starbucks other than you know what you are going to receive wherever you visit one of these fine coffee shops.  Nice staff, clean restaurant, a little cramped, but that's because lots of people like this place and they tend to linger.  Nice breakfast selections and tasty pastries.
